The bathroom was big, with plenty of fluffy towels and the bedroom had a large TV with a good selection of channels.	The room was well appointed with two double beds, big LCD TV (some English channels), huge bathroom with bidet, separate area for sink and tub w/shower, lots of desk space.	One thing we find missing in the room - the complimentary coffee and tea, or at least an electric kettle.	Cleanliness scored four out of five as the carpet in the hall /corridor had a few spots, but the room was large and cosy (we had a standard double) and TV had a nice selection of international / EU channels (but also CNN).